<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Storyboard: renders an end-to-end recording with every frame type</title>
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="https://http4k.org/favicon-32.png">
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="https://http4k.org/favicon-16.png">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
<style>
:root {
    --color-text: #212529;
    --color-text-muted: #6c757d;
    --color-border: #dee2e6;
    --color-bg-light: #f8f9fa;
    --color-bg-hover: #e9ecef;
    --color-accent: #fd7e14;
    --color-link: #0d6efd;
}
* { box-sizing: border-box; }
html, body { height: 100%; }
body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
    background: #fff;
    color: var(--color-text);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
}
.app-header {
    background: url("https://http4k.org/images/pipes-hero.svg"), linear-gradient(135deg, #59AFF5 0%, #2096F3 50%, #61C0FF 100%);
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    padding: 14px 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-shrink: 0;
}
.app-header-brand { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
.app-logo { height: 36px; }
.app-header-title { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: #fff; }
h1.test-title { margin: 0; padding: 12px 20px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-text); background: var(--color-bg-light); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); flex-shrink: 0; display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
h1.test-title .test-breadcrumb { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
h1.test-title a.test-breadcrumb:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
h1.test-title .test-sep { color: var(--color-text-muted); font-weight: 400; }
h1.test-title .test-heading { font-weight: 500; }
footer.app-footer { text-align: center; padding: 10px 0; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); background: var(--color-bg-light); flex-shrink: 0; }
footer.app-footer a { color: var(--color-text-muted); }
.mode-toggle { display: inline-flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center; }
.mode-toggle .btn-group {
    position: relative;
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 999px;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: inline-flex;
}
.mode-toggle .btn-group::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    transform: translateY(100%);
    transition: transform 0.25s ease;
    z-index: 0;
}
.mode-toggle .btn-group:has(.btn-check:checked)::before { transform: translateY(0); }
.mode-toggle .btn {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    font-size: 11px;
    padding: 4px 14px;
    text-align: center;
    background: transparent !important;
    border: 0 !important;
    border-radius: 999px !important;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    transition: color 0.25s ease;
    box-shadow: none !important;
}
.mode-toggle .btn-check:checked + .btn { color: #fff; }
body:has(#mode-story:checked) [data-level="Context"],
body:has(#mode-story:checked) [data-level="Detail"] { display: none; }
body:has(#mode-context:checked) [data-level="Detail"] { display: none; }
body { font-size: 14px; overflow-y: auto; }
.flat-mode-bar { position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 10; background: var(--color-bg-light); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding: 8px 16px; display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; }
main.flat-view { flex: 1; padding: 24px; max-width: 1080px; width: 100%; margin: 0 auto; }
main.flat-view section.chapter { margin-bottom: 32px; padding-left: 0; }
main.flat-view section.chapter.depth-2, main.flat-view section.chapter.depth-3, main.flat-view section.chapter.depth-4 { padding-left: 18px; border-left: 2px solid var(--color-border); }
main.flat-view section.chapter > h2, main.flat-view section.chapter > h3, main.flat-view section.chapter > h4, main.flat-view section.chapter > h5, main.flat-view section.chapter > h6 { margin: 4px 0 16px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-text); }
main.flat-view section.chapter > h2 { font-size: 22px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding-bottom: 6px; }
main.flat-view section.chapter > h3 { font-size: 18px; color: var(--color-text-muted); }
main.flat-view section.chapter > h4 { font-size: 16px; color: var(--color-text-muted); }
article.frame { margin: 0 0 20px; padding: 12px 14px; background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 6px; }
article.frame > header { display: flex; align-items: baseline; justify-content: space-between; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
article.frame > header .title { font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; color: var(--color-text); }
article.frame > header .level { font-size: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: var(--color-text-muted); padding: 2px 8px; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 999px; }
article.frame .notes { margin: 0 0 10px; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 13px; font-style: italic; }
article.frame .capture-frame { width: 100%; height: 420px; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 4px; background: #fff; }
article.frame pre.code-block { margin: 0; padding: 10px; border-radius: 4px; background: #f6f8fa; font-size: 12px; overflow-x: auto; }
</style>

</head>
<body>
<header class="app-header">
    <div class="app-header-brand">
        <a href="https://http4k.org" target="_blank"><img class="app-logo" src="https://http4k.org/images/logo.png" alt="Storyboard"></a>
        <span class="app-header-title">Storyboard</span>
    </div>
</header>
<h1 class="test-title">
    <a class="test-breadcrumb" href="index.html">EndToEndFlatTest</a><span class="test-sep">›</span>
    <span class="test-heading">renders an end-to-end recording with every frame type</span>
</h1>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/themes/prism.min.css">
<div class="flat-mode-bar"><div class="mode-toggle" role="group" aria-label="Detail level">
    <div class="btn-group">
        <input type="radio" class="btn-check" name="mode" id="mode-story" autocomplete="off" checked>
        <label class="btn" for="mode-story">Story</label>
    </div>
    <div class="btn-group">
        <input type="radio" class="btn-check" name="mode" id="mode-context" autocomplete="off" >
        <label class="btn" for="mode-context">Context</label>
    </div>
    <div class="btn-group">
        <input type="radio" class="btn-check" name="mode" id="mode-detail" autocomplete="off" >
        <label class="btn" for="mode-detail">Detail</label>
    </div>
</div>
</div>
<main class="flat-view">
    <section class="chapter depth-1">
        <h2>renders an end-to-end recording with every frame type</h2>
        
        
        
        
            <article class="frame" data-type="image" data-level="Story">
                <header>
                    <span class="title">Sample image</span>
                    <span class="level">Story</span>
                </header>
                
                    <iframe class="capture-frame" sandbox="" data-dom=""></iframe>
            </article>
    <section class="chapter depth-2">
        
        <h3>Setup</h3>
        
        
        
            <article class="frame" data-type="html" data-level="Context">
                <header>
                    <span class="title">Splash</span>
                    <span class="level">Context</span>
                </header>
                
                    <iframe class="capture-frame" sandbox="allow-scripts" data-dom=""></iframe>
            </article>
            <article class="frame" data-type="code" data-level="Context">
                <header>
                    <span class="title">Sample source</span>
                    <span class="level">Context</span>
                </header>
                
                    <pre class="code-block"><code class="language-kotlin">fun greet(name: String) = &quot;hello, $name&quot;
fun farewell(name: String) = &quot;goodbye, $name&quot;
</code></pre>
            </article>
    </section>
    <section class="chapter depth-2">
        
        <h3>Run</h3>
        
        
        
            <article class="frame" data-type="code" data-level="Detail">
                <header>
                    <span class="title">postgresql SELECT</span>
                    <span class="level">Detail</span>
                </header>
                
                    <pre class="code-block"><code class="language-sql">SELECT message FROM greetings WHERE id = 1</code></pre>
            </article>
            <article class="frame" data-type="html" data-level="Detail">
                <header>
                    <span class="title">SERVER GET data</span>
                    <span class="level">Detail</span>
                </header>
                
                    <iframe class="capture-frame" sandbox="allow-scripts" data-dom=""></iframe>
            </article>
            <article class="frame" data-type="html" data-level="Detail">
                <header>
                    <span class="title">CLIENT GET /data</span>
                    <span class="level">Detail</span>
                </header>
                
                    <iframe class="capture-frame" sandbox="allow-scripts" data-dom=""></iframe>
            </article>
            <article class="frame" data-type="html" data-level="Detail">
                <header>
                    <span class="title">SERVER GET home</span>
                    <span class="level">Detail</span>
                </header>
                
                    <iframe class="capture-frame" sandbox="allow-scripts" data-dom=""></iframe>
            </article>
            <article class="frame" data-type="html" data-level="Detail">
                <header>
                    <span class="title">CLIENT GET /home</span>
                    <span class="level">Detail</span>
                </header>
                
                    <iframe class="capture-frame" sandbox="allow-scripts" data-dom=""></iframe>
            </article>
            <article class="frame" data-type="webdrivercapture" data-level="Story">
                <header>
                    <span class="title">Home</span>
                    <span class="level">Story</span>
                </header>
                <p class="notes">first navigation</p>
                    <iframe class="capture-frame" sandbox="" data-dom="PCFET0NUWVBFIGh0bWw+CjxodG1sPjxoZWFkPjx0aXRsZT5Ib21lPC90aXRsZT48L2hlYWQ+Cjxib2R5PgogIDxoMT5XZWxjb21lPC9oMT4KICA8cD5Mb2FkZWQgZnJvbSBpbm5lciBzZXJ2aWNlOiA8c3Ryb25nPmhlbGxvIGlubmVyPC9zdHJvbmc+PC9wPgogIDxhIGlkPSJuZXh0IiBocmVmPSIvZGV0YWlsIj5nbyBkZWVwZXI8L2E+CjwvYm9keT48L2h0bWw+"></iframe>
            </article>
    <section class="chapter depth-3">
        
        
        <h4>Detail</h4>
        
        
            <article class="frame" data-type="code" data-level="Detail">
                <header>
                    <span class="title">postgresql SELECT</span>
                    <span class="level">Detail</span>
                </header>
                
                    <pre class="code-block"><code class="language-sql">SELECT message FROM greetings WHERE id = 1</code></pre>
            </article>
            <article class="frame" data-type="html" data-level="Detail">
                <header>
                    <span class="title">SERVER GET data</span>
                    <span class="level">Detail</span>
                </header>
                
                    <iframe class="capture-frame" sandbox="allow-scripts" data-dom=""></iframe>
            </article>
            <article class="frame" data-type="html" data-level="Detail">
                <header>
                    <span class="title">CLIENT GET /data</span>
                    <span class="level">Detail</span>
                </header>
                
                    <iframe class="capture-frame" sandbox="allow-scripts" data-dom=""></iframe>
            </article>
            <article class="frame" data-type="html" data-level="Detail">
                <header>
                    <span class="title">SERVER GET detail</span>
                    <span class="level">Detail</span>
                </header>
                
                    <iframe class="capture-frame" sandbox="allow-scripts" data-dom=""></iframe>
            </article>
            <article class="frame" data-type="html" data-level="Detail">
                <header>
                    <span class="title">CLIENT GET /detail</span>
                    <span class="level">Detail</span>
                </header>
                
                    <iframe class="capture-frame" sandbox="allow-scripts" data-dom=""></iframe>
            </article>
            <article class="frame" data-type="webdrivercapture" data-level="Detail">
                <header>
                    <span class="title">click [By.id: next]</span>
                    <span class="level">Detail</span>
                </header>
                
                    <iframe class="capture-frame" sandbox="" data-dom="PCFET0NUWVBFIGh0bWw+CjxodG1sPjxoZWFkPjx0aXRsZT5EZXRhaWw8L3RpdGxlPjwvaGVhZD4KPGJvZHk+CiAgPGgxPkRldGFpbCBwYWdlPC9oMT4KICA8cD5EZXRhaWwgZGF0YTogPGVtPmhlbGxvIGlubmVyPC9lbT48L3A+CjwvYm9keT48L2h0bWw+"></iframe>
            </article>
            <article class="frame" data-type="webdrivercapture" data-level="Story">
                <header>
                    <span class="title">Detail page</span>
                    <span class="level">Story</span>
                </header>
                <p class="notes">after the click</p>
                    <iframe class="capture-frame" sandbox="" data-dom="PCFET0NUWVBFIGh0bWw+CjxodG1sPjxoZWFkPjx0aXRsZT5EZXRhaWw8L3RpdGxlPjwvaGVhZD4KPGJvZHk+CiAgPGgxPkRldGFpbCBwYWdlPC9oMT4KICA8cD5EZXRhaWwgZGF0YTogPGVtPmhlbGxvIGlubmVyPC9lbT48L3A+CjwvYm9keT48L2h0bWw+"></iframe>
            </article>
    </section>
    </section>
    <section class="chapter depth-2">
        
        <h3>Wrap-up</h3>
        
        
        
            <article class="frame" data-type="html" data-level="Context">
                <header>
                    <span class="title">Outro</span>
                    <span class="level">Context</span>
                </header>
                
                    <iframe class="capture-frame" sandbox="allow-scripts" data-dom=""></iframe>
            </article>
    </section>
    </section>
</main>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/prism.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/plugins/autoloader/prism-autoloader.min.js"></script>
<script>
document.querySelectorAll('iframe.capture-frame[data-dom]').forEach(f => {
    f.srcdoc = atob(f.getAttribute('data-dom'));
});
</script>
<footer class="app-footer">
    Generated by http4k Storyboard · <a href="https://http4k.org" target="_blank">http4k.org</a>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
